{"tid":1690375,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"沙田警員帶走多人　有警員指市民「壞咗個腦無得救」","createTime":"2019-11-03T09:48:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-04T04:18:09.000Z","uid":184679,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"cba22fcc9b2588e55a53efc402154e0af27d45e4","tid":1690375,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T09:48:46.000Z","msg":"網上有人發起下午在多個地區進行「行街」活動反對警暴，警方加強佈防。其中沙田大會堂百步梯有約100人聚集，多人被制服帶走。<br />\n<br />\n有目擊者表示，下午約1時40分，數名男子在百步梯旁推撞，10多名市民圍觀，至少有3人被制服。<br />\n<br />\n數十名防暴警員隨即增援，進入大會堂公園再制服約5人，並帶上警車，並截查多名市民搜身。有在場警員表示，從被制服人士搜到鎚仔等工具，有警員就以粗言指罵身處平台聚集的市民，不滿有人向下投擲水樽。<br />\n<br />\n期間有市民一度與警員就執法問題理論，有警員向市民說「不要再提及7.21」，又警告該名市民不要再煽動其他人。另一名警察帶走同袍時說市民「壞咗個腦無得救」，市民起哄。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1489808-20191103.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1489808-20191103.htm&d=AnzAvEp6rraOVT5%2FQxAiQRFNIXSBonesC3SPsSCGYVE%3D&h=41472138\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1489808-20191103.htm&h=b9ba91aa\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1489808-20191103.htm</a>"},{"pid":"2ff8e4aa0f1353ac2372367d43a1f3de2c327fc4","tid":1690375,"uid":145273,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T09:50:57.000Z","msg":"點解唔可以提7.21？你哋心虛啊？"},{"pid":"0dab18c6307e98845c9b04562a4fc1c01f374f7e","tid":1690375,"uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T09:52:07.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">721<br />\n<br />\n721<br />\n<br />\n721</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"17482191a0dc8f9bd1d3214dca9f0b63fa318fb6","tid":1690375,"uid":235015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T09:53:20.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"6fe64bd6354ae7f0fc12b9937836f2f0532ccce1","tid":1690375,"uid":57674,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":